criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. Meet the diagnostic criteria of grade II-IV mixed hemorrhoids and meet the operation
             conditions;

          2. Age 18~65;

          3. External stripping and internal ligation of mixed hemorrhoids, general anesthesia or
             lumbar shu point anesthesia;

          4. VAS score ≥3 points;

          5. Sign informed consent.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Combined cognitive impairment could not complete the efficacy evaluation;

          -  With other gastrointestinal conditions found during operation;

          -  With severe cardiovascular, hepatic, or renal diseases;

          -  With opioid addiction
